      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DARK MONEY (1) has a solid record despite not breaking through for a win in six starts. Hit the frame again last start finishing second (18.64) at this track. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Top prospect. SPRING MAISIE (5) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Well Read (23.27) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Hard to beat again. WOLFMAN SID (6) makes his debut without a trial but profiles well for first outing. Among the leading players. ZIPPING LAWSON (8) is a newcomer from the Courtney Barnes kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can sneak into the frame at his first appearance.",
